<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section 7303 requires seamen to retain their merchant mariner’s documents. It also specifies the information that is to be contained in the document.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idf67a601c-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
